    <li><strong>Apparel Printing:</strong> From hoodies to tank tops, we offer a variety of apparel printing options to fit your needs.</li>
    <li><strong>Specialty Inks & Effects:</strong> Take your designs to the next level with metallic inks, puff prints, glow-in-the-dark, and other specialty effects.</li>
