    <li><i class="underline-text">Schools & Universities:</i><br>Spirit wear, club t-shirts, and sports team apparel.</li><br>
    <li><i class="underline-text">Event Organizers:</i><br>Custom apparel for concerts, festivals, charity events, and fundraisers.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

