<div class="flex justify-center items-center text-center">
  <ol class="max-w-lg">
    <li><i class="underline-text">Submit Your Design:</i> <br>Upload your artwork or work with our designers to create something unique.</li><br>
    <li><i class="underline-text">Choose Your Apparel:</i> <br>Select from a wide range of high-quality garments and materials.</li><br>
    <li><i class="underline-text">Approve Your Proof:</i> <br>We provide digital mockups for your approval before production.</li><br>
    <li><i class="underline-text">Production & Delivery:</i> <br>Once approved, we print and deliver your order quickly and efficiently.</li>
  </ol>
</div>


